title: Super Duper Comics # 3
description:
Canadian golden age comic book that despite the # number probably is the only book in a non-existing series

Published by F.E. Howard Publications Ltd 1947

This is sparkling pop-art, slick in style and colors, and definately pre-code in content

Features odd muppets like Nelvana of the Northern Lights, Jeff Waring, Java Beans, Tang, Cinder Smith and most notably, the first appearence of Mr. Monster, the character Michael T. Gilbert would revive in the 80's
